  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/0cdb3608f16a182929ef3d41dd613803.avif?t=1744717806\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras_big/0cdb3608f16a182929ef3d41dd613803.avif?t=1744717806 width=800 height=235 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TOY SCRAPPERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique multiplayer horror and escape game for 2 to 16 players! Become a crazy clown and hunt down your prey, or play as a toy and try to survive the madness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/de85fd890f3b3c3f6bb6cda2cebb12a4.poster.avif?t=1744717806\" width=800 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/de85fd890f3b3c3f6bb6cda2cebb12a4.webm?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/de85fd890f3b3c3f6bb6cda2cebb12a4.mp4?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE MADNESS, STAY ALIVE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a toy caught in the middle of crazy clowns, hide and try to stay alive without being caught. Increase your chances of survival with special abilities!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decoy</strong>: Create a copy of yourself to confuse your pursuers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prop</strong>: Turn into an object and blend into your surroundings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Illusion</strong>: Spawn 8 copies of yourself to vanish in the chaos!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invisibility</strong>: Disappear completely and escape without a trace!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/19328266f41f2ccb6a412227e9251f26.poster.avif?t=1744717806\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/19328266f41f2ccb6a412227e9251f26.webm?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/19328266f41f2ccb6a412227e9251f26.mp4?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME A CRAZY CLOWN!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a clown, your goal is to find the hidden toys on the map. Hunt them down and turn them to your side! Use your special abilities to trap them!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trap</strong>: Place a trap on the ground and wait for them to get caught!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sense</strong>: Feel nearby enemies and locate them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/95e3ce144df4817c615cd235fb436a0f.poster.avif?t=1744717806\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/95e3ce144df4817c615cd235fb436a0f.webm?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/95e3ce144df4817c615cd235fb436a0f.mp4?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOY SCRAPPERS</strong> offers an unforgettable experience filled with laughter and thrills to share with friends. <strong>Will you be the hunter or the hunted?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/0cdb3608f16a182929ef3d41dd613803.avif?t=1744717806\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras_big/0cdb3608f16a182929ef3d41dd613803.avif?t=1744717806 width=800 height=235 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TOY SCRAPPERS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique multiplayer horror and escape game for 2 to 16 players! Become a crazy clown and hunt down your prey, or play as a toy and try to survive the madness!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/de85fd890f3b3c3f6bb6cda2cebb12a4.poster.avif?t=1744717806\" width=800 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/de85fd890f3b3c3f6bb6cda2cebb12a4.webm?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/de85fd890f3b3c3f6bb6cda2cebb12a4.mp4?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE MADNESS, STAY ALIVE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a toy caught in the middle of crazy clowns, hide and try to stay alive without being caught. Increase your chances of survival with special abilities!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decoy</strong>: Create a copy of yourself to confuse your pursuers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prop</strong>: Turn into an object and blend into your surroundings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Illusion</strong>: Spawn 8 copies of yourself to vanish in the chaos!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invisibility</strong>: Disappear completely and escape without a trace!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/19328266f41f2ccb6a412227e9251f26.poster.avif?t=1744717806\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/19328266f41f2ccb6a412227e9251f26.webm?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/19328266f41f2ccb6a412227e9251f26.mp4?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME A CRAZY CLOWN!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a clown, your goal is to find the hidden toys on the map. Hunt them down and turn them to your side! Use your special abilities to trap them!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Trap</strong>: Place a trap on the ground and wait for them to get caught!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sense</strong>: Feel nearby enemies and locate them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/95e3ce144df4817c615cd235fb436a0f.poster.avif?t=1744717806\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/95e3ce144df4817c615cd235fb436a0f.webm?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3457790/extras/95e3ce144df4817c615cd235fb436a0f.mp4?t=1744717806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOY SCRAPPERS</strong> offers an unforgettable experience filled with laughter and thrills to share with friends. <strong>Will you be the hunter or the hunted?</strong></p>",
